title: Unblack Metal 21 Albums Antestor Crimson Moonlight etc pt 2 of 3
description:
Dear Boss,


*************


This torrent is the fifth of mine.  Now that I am back I don't have to put up a front.  Data isn't just androgynous; it is good for the taking.  Not too much wine now, slow down.  Save room for dessert.


*************


I believe in quality torrents; if for any reason you do not find this torrent to be satisfactory, please let me know in the comments.  If you like this music please support the artist(s) and purchase it!  If the album is out of print, please support the artist by buying releases that are not out of print, or by buying merchandise from their official store.  The contents of this torrent are for sampling purposes only.  Enjoy!


*************


Due to the underground nature of Christian unblack metal, I have decided to put together some torrents to give you an opportunity to sample the material.  This is part two in a series of three torrents, all containing 7 albums each (for the number of perfection, 777).  Each torrent will also contain a bonus album or EP.  This is a great collection; I hope you enjoy it.  Bit rate is highest when possible.  I WILL ONLY RELEASE PART THREE IF PEOPLE SEED.  YOU KNOW WHAT THAT MEANS.  Thanks to everyone who continues to seed part one.


*************
